    <div>
      <p class="eyebrow">In Loving Memory</p>
      <h2>The Amanda Forum</h2>
      <p style="margin-top:16px">Established in summer 2013 following the death of local teenager Amanda Bach, who died from teen dating violence, The Amanda Forum raises awareness of youth dating violence and relationship red flags in Porter County through discussion, education, and mentoring.</p>
      <ul class="checklist">
        <li>Healthy relationship skills and recognizing red flags</li>
        <li>Coping with breakups in constructive ways</li>
        <li>Building resilience and protective factors</li>
        <li>For teens, college students, parents, and the wider community</li>
      </ul>
      <p style="margin-top:12px">The task force hosts conferences with nationally known speakers, produces the "No Broken Boundaries" podcast, and shares educational materials for families and teens.</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas" style="margin-top:26px">
        <a class="btn btn-teal" href="{{ '/contact/' | url }}">Request the Amanda Forum for your school or group</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
